[vc_row row_type="2" blox_height="340" blox_image="6359" blox_cover="false" page_title="page-title-x" blox_dark="true"][vc_column][distance type="5"][distance type="5"][vc_column_text]

CMSHOSTING

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][distance type="4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][subtitle subtitle_content="Easy Host Provides the Best in CMS Hosting"][vc_column_text]Content Management System, shortly referred to as CMS, is a web hosting system that allows you to define and set permissions for multiple users at various levels to handle and manage the different sections of content in your website. The content can fall under different kinds of classifications such as articles, blogs, events, press releases and many more. When a fine line is drawn, the Content Management System falls in two categories called the Traditional or Open Source Content Management Systems and the Hosted CMS. If you have chosen to use Joomla, WordPress, Drupal or another Content Management Systems (CMS) to create your website, you can count on our unique handmade hosting solution. We will make sure that the CMS of your choice runs smoothly on our servers and that your website is safer, faster and better supported than anywhere else![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="6406" img_size="full"][/vc_column][vc_column][distance type="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="5/12" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="6410" img_size="full"][/vc_column][vc_column width="7/12"][distance][vc_column_text]

WordPress Hosting

WordPress was initially started for blogging purpose, but in the long run it has gained success as a Content Management System as well. WordPress is the worlds most popular website building tool. It gives you access to thousands of free themes and plug-in that help simplify the design process.[/vc_column_text][button shape="rounded" btn_content="Read more" url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/host/cms-hosting-wordpress/" color="gray" size="medium" border="true"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column][distance type="3"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="7/12"][distance][vc_column_text]

Joomla Hosting

Joomla is yet another CMS that is mobile ready and user friendly. Today Joomla counts for more than 35 million downloads. Joomla also offers a huge number of extensions to add additional features. Our hosting solutions are tailor-made for optimal security and performance! In fact our Joomla hosting is mirrored, providing our business users with a unique fail-safe system.[/vc_column_text][button shape="rounded" btn_content="Read more" url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/host/cms-hosting-joomla/" color="gray" size="medium" border="true"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="6417" img_size="full"][/vc_column][vc_column][distance type="3"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="5/12" offset="vc_hidden-xs"][vc_single_image image="9418" img_size="full"][/vc_column][vc_column width="7/12"][distance][vc_column_text]

Drupal Hosting

Drupal is a very popular and flexible Content Management System available in the market. Though it is quite simple to use, it would be better to handle it with a prior knowledge of coding and other technical aspects. We are leader in Drupal hosting, We currently host hundreds of Drupal-based sites and blogs.[/vc_column_text][button shape="rounded" btn_content="Read more" url="http://webnus.biz/themes/easyweb/host/cms-hosting-drupal/" color="gray" size="medium" border="true"][distance][/vc_column][vc_column][distance type="3"][/vc_column][/vc_row]
